LUCY M. DURFEY v. EUSTACE G. WATTS 25 So. (2nd) 200

January Term, 1946

March 8, 1946 Division A Morton B. Adams, for appellant. Eugene A. Williams and Ernest A. Roth, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

Only questions of fact are raised on this appeal which were decided adversely to appellant by the master in chancery ■ and the chancellor. We find no error in the decree, so it is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
